{"tid":520834,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話歐遊一定洗費貴 8日扮土豪波蘭之旅","createTime":"2018-01-05T22:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T03:12:29.000Z","uid":7049,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"08265a3c33d152fb0e859f14966bab3f19500a09","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T22:21:45.000Z","msg":"聽日又係Bank Holiday喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面又係乜都唔開<br />\n咁不如打下遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家係Gdańsk 下星期一先走<br />\n之前去左<br />\nBydgoszcz同Warsaw<br />\n<br />\n如果計劃緊去歐洲既巴絲 不妨去埋波蘭 真係幾抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n物價同車費又平 不過係d人唔係個個識英文同有時黑口黑面 或者見你係亞洲人會好好奇望住你 上次係tram個司機仲要同我地揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n治安感覺上比西歐好 暫時冇財物損失 都冇乜點見homeless<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依度消費真係好平呀 好想賴死唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"68657f93836c73477e865e964a391abfd5e6e0bf","tid":520834,"uid":93620,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"係人都知東歐平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6dd9eeed02a777d2b82b28aaa10e12cb43bc0","tid":520834,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"波蘭奧地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2901d648af5fffd10174535e7520d9cb689426c5","tid":520834,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"428706ba2b8099b50424078d7ba01cad72341c41","tid":520834,"uid":81037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"點解只去一個國家"},{"pid":"671de54c377ab31a8e4686d101c6c80f560849cb","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"PLN 1 : HKD ~2.2<br />\n電話卡<br />\n出發前記得check定邊度有得買電話卡/租wifi蛋<br />\n而家波蘭電話卡要實名制 <br />\n佢地門市放晒工既話就要過住冇data用既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依度電話卡好抵用<br />\n電信商比較多見既有 PLAY / T mobile / Orange<br />\n建議去門市買 油站便利店都有 但都要行多次去門市登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n需要文件：Poland Sim card + Passport<br />\n我fd買果張係PLAY 3GB 9PLN (~20hkd)<br />\n其他都大約5PLN~10PLN 唔夠可以再top up<br />\n<br />\n唱錢<br />\n我見唔多找換店會唱HKD<br />\n建議唱做EURO/USD先<br />\n不過有間找換店個叔叔好好人<br />\n肯幫我唱住先 佢再第日去同第間換<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ef8d8ce89ecb3b63b82d684e6f47b6f2b77405","tid":520834,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c3936b9c0c3263eee89e5202720827e5c9ccb0b2","tid":520834,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139d4d584fa6fbeef09aafc3b97ea9ffdf22a50f","tid":520834,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"留名學野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c415226983bc9f71caed28a51d4f4b432e4c282","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"而家係波蘭既北邊 睇緊個海 今晚繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfec0f635db9581e85567b68997a9c765c96d6f7","tid":520834,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"63bb38cced5721a42440314f43ad00bb544a9ab6","tid":520834,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"留名 想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb85e30f9dc0a889010395458980a9e60c94c72","tid":520834,"uid":157828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"遲下都會去Gdańsk，留名學野"},{"pid":"472f636a2060fc0302c3318db8f21cf5a9c90860","tid":520834,"uid":132859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"波蘭妹# <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波蘭真係人傑地靈<br />\n可惜之前去係同屋企人一齊跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望遲下可以自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade66697c1570a354f06c11abf7db2457a887072","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdb85e30f9dc0a889010395458980a9e60c94c72","tid":520834,"uid":157828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"遲下都會去Gdańsk，留名學野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"真心高汁 個人黎講覺得靚過華沙<br />\n本身黎依個城市係因為機票平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef43a79d920adcb8b7de8a2669ce18e10823135","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/t7v0Tb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Ft7v0Tb.png&h=3acd8115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現新版3310<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依度好d人好鐘意用華為機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b685f1916750f5b4898d042c8b3dfe2506708241","tid":520834,"uid":106579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"留名 想睇圖 希望有機會去"},{"pid":"aa5cbf56636a23e92ed64bb8b4d5e9f6be14f765","tid":520834,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"649d509baa1d4418a2cf61185278192ec6c0eac5","tid":520834,"uid":131714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"790a77f5f13620ca7fc5a21097721884bf6ef11f","tid":520834,"uid":3050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"上年6月去過做野一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇有咩玩"},{"pid":"6c1769c0ec2d54f61e1e7ed29b6a1df024ec296f","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"790a77f5f13620ca7fc5a21097721884bf6ef11f","tid":520834,"uid":3050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"上年6月去過做野一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇有咩玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"飲飲食食咋 講玩都係冇乜野好玩既<br />\n買下野咁 日日訓到自然醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁先係旅行架ma"},{"pid":"faa3d8df6539db035efd77ea2e7f497fddb6e3e3","tid":520834,"uid":59394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"30f451c732e3a4b1d0236a23b00bfbf3e9b9626d","tid":520834,"uid":100934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c415226983bc9f71caed28a51d4f4b432e4c282","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"而家係波蘭既北邊 睇緊個海 今晚繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:12:05.000Z","msg":"Hel?個度超靚，一世都會記住咁靚既海灘<br />\n利申：7年前去過"},{"pid":"6ea01628f0bffaff8ea9da7a248e5c725b88359a","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:19:51.000Z","msg":"Day 1 Bydgoszcz<br />\n<br />\n由London Luton Airport飛過去 約2個鐘度，<br />\n落機過入境個時個人，望住香港passport 再打左幾個電話，問左好多問題先比入境 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出到機場，竟然冇的士！<br />\n都冇電信商買電話卡，的士亦都唔會駛過黎，因為個個都趕住去除夕party<br />\n<br />\n好彩有個好心既當地人話比我地知可以搭巴士去酒店，<br />\n同行有一對由巴西黎既家庭，落車先發現原來我地住同一間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上車可以同巴士司機買飛，但要準備散子，或者見到賣飛既機就買定先，亦都可以唔買飛，但比人check飛既風險自行承擔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為除夕既關係，好多餐廳都唔開，最後係食油站既熱狗... (6.xxPLN)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/R1psxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FR1psxD.png&h=008fdc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又幾好味咁喎...但好似碌...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相信大家都唔會黎依度 所以係依個城市既野就唔多講<br />\n<del>我都係貪機票平先黎架咋，我意不在此</del><br />\n<br />\n但好開心，雖然出唔到去倒數，但可以係窗門睇<br />\n等到12點 樓下有人放煙花呀！！！<br />\n見到咁緊係即刻狗衝落去睇，並且獲得兩個波蘭嬸嬸既香吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/cFXPuC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FcFXPuC.png&h=e90db885&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/IYtzDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FIYtzDA.png&h=b136ba3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/3FByDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F3FByDg.png&h=5be0839c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eb0e2cb85f3aa836aaf2f19425132bce2553bf3","tid":520834,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:26:56.000Z","msg":"天氣凍唔凍?"},{"pid":"212014272febaafc14d31b4a9c13bb3a22a13c2f","tid":520834,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eb0e2cb85f3aa836aaf2f19425132bce2553bf3","tid":520834,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:26:56.000Z","msg":"天氣凍唔凍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:30:55.000Z","msg":"又唔會好凍 冇落雪 但落雨<br />\n而家4度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n著緊冷衫加頸巾"},{"pid":"fd1ef73c7ec88c2f38086b1be686e795dcbeb2f2","tid":520834,"uid":874